title: World of Warcraft Soundtrack Collection
description:
World of Warcraft Soundtrack Collection

This is a collection of music from World of Warcraft (and Warcraft III) which I've compiled over the years from multiple sources.
It includes every WoW expansions accompanying soundtracks (along with a few mini soundtracks and special compilations), as well as the Warcraft III soundtrack and it's expansions soundtrack as well.
Invincible can be found on the Fall of the Lich King album, as the last track, since it can sometimes be hard to find.
Everything is also fully ID3 tagged, 320kbps and has album artwork.
Enjoy!
